  Datasets to use:
  - InLegalBench — Indian legal Q&A benchmark (primary)
  - LegalBench — general legal reasoning (secondary)
  - ILDC (Indian Legal Document Corpus) — for summarizer training/eval
  - CUAD — contract understanding (for commercial adapter)
  - Your own eval set — 100 expert-verified Q&A pairs per domain (build as you go)

